@startuml
title UC-07. Посмотреть SLA и uptime

actor "Пользователь / руководитель" as User
participant "Monitoring API" as API
participant "Result & SLA Module" as ResultSLA
database "Monitoring DB" as DB

User -> API: GET /api/v1/services/{serviceId}/stats?period=month
API -> ResultSLA: calculateMonthlyStats(serviceId)

ResultSLA -> DB: SELECT service WHERE id = serviceId
DB --> ResultSLA: service with sla_target_percent

ResultSLA -> DB: SELECT check_result\nWHERE service_id = serviceId\nAND checked_at in current month
DB --> ResultSLA: monthly check results

ResultSLA -> ResultSLA: total_checks = count(*)
ResultSLA -> ResultSLA: up_checks = count(status = 'UP')
ResultSLA -> ResultSLA: down_checks = count(status = 'DOWN')
ResultSLA -> ResultSLA: uptime_percent = up_checks / total_checks * 100
ResultSLA -> ResultSLA: sla_breached = uptime_percent < sla_target_percent

ResultSLA --> API: monthly SLA stats
API --> User: 200 OK + uptime/SLA

@enduml